#: ui/tabs/drivers_tab.py:356
msgid "Legacy Driver Support Required"
msgstr "Legacy Driver Support Required"

#: ui/tabs/drivers_tab.py:360
msgid ""
"This legacy driver is only available in the unstable repositories.\n"
"\n"
"We will now open <b>Soplos Repo Selector</b> so you can temporarily enable "
"the <b>Debian Sid (Unstable)</b> repository.\n"
"\n"
"After completing the driver installation, it is CRITICAL that you return to "
"Soplos Repo Selector and disable Sid, or you may break your system during "
"future updates.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to enable Sid and continue with the installation?"
msgstr ""
"This legacy driver is only available in the unstable repositories.\n"
"\n"
"We will now open <b>Soplos Repo Selector</b> so you can temporarily enable "
"the <b>Debian Sid (Unstable)</b> repository.\n"
"\n"
"After completing the driver installation, it is CRITICAL that you return to "
"Soplos Repo Selector and disable Sid, or you may break your system during "
"future updates.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to enable Sid and continue with the installation?"

#: ui/tabs/drivers_tab.py:387
msgid "Waiting for Soplos Repo Selector"
msgstr "Waiting for Soplos Repo Selector"

#: ui/tabs/drivers_tab.py:391
msgid ""
"Soplos Repo Selector has been opened.\n"
"\n"
"1. Enable the <b>Debian Sid (Unstable)</b> repository.\n"
"2. Wait for the operation to finish and close Soplos Repo Selector.\n"
"3. Click <b>OK</b> below to begin the driver installation.\n"
"\n"
"If you changed your mind, click Cancel."
msgstr ""
"Soplos Repo Selector has been opened.\n"
"\n"
"1. Enable the <b>Debian Sid (Unstable)</b> repository.\n"
"2. Wait for the operation to finish and close Soplos Repo Selector.\n"
"3. Click <b>OK</b> below to begin the driver installation.\n"
"\n"
"If you changed your mind, click Cancel."
#: ui/tabs/drivers_tab.py:415
msgid "Confirm NVIDIA Driver Installation"
msgstr "Confirm NVIDIA Driver Installation"

#: ui/tabs/drivers_tab.py:418
msgid ""
"This will:\n"
"\n"
"1. Remove any existing NVIDIA drivers to prevent conflicts.\n"
"2. Install the driver: {package}\n"
"3. Install auxiliary tools (nvidia-smi, nvidia-settings).\n"
"4. Regenerate initramfs.\n"
"\n"
"A system restart will be required after installation.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to continue?"
msgstr ""
"This will:\n"
"\n"
"1. Remove any existing NVIDIA drivers to prevent conflicts.\n"
"2. Install the driver: {package}\n"
"3. Install auxiliary tools (nvidia-smi, nvidia-settings).\n"
"4. Regenerate initramfs.\n"
"\n"
"A system restart will be required after installation.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to continue?"

#: ui/tabs/drivers_tab.py:494
msgid "Confirm NVIDIA CUDA Driver Installation"
msgstr "Confirm NVIDIA CUDA Driver Installation"

#: ui/tabs/drivers_tab.py:497
msgid ""
"This will:\n"
"\n"
"1. Remove any existing NVIDIA drivers to prevent conflicts.\n"
"2. Add the official NVIDIA CUDA repository.\n"
"3. Install driver version {version} with auxiliary tools.\n"
"4. Regenerate initramfs.\n"
"\n"
"A system restart will be required after installation.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to continue?"
msgstr ""
"This will:\n"
"\n"
"1. Remove any existing NVIDIA drivers to prevent conflicts.\n"
"2. Add the official NVIDIA CUDA repository.\n"
"3. Install driver version {version} with auxiliary tools.\n"
"4. Regenerate initramfs.\n"
"\n"
"A system restart will be required after installation.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to continue?"
